Package lib.model

Class Interaction

java.lang.Object
lib.model.Interaction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Has_Copy<Interaction>, Has_ID
public class Interaction extends Object implements Has_ID, Has_Copy<Interaction>
A class that describes social media interactions. Users can post, comment on each other's posts, and like and share each other's posts (whether they are root comments or child comments).
